prod.desciption: The women's Nike Dunk Low SE Easter Candy (W) features a white leather upper with asymmetrical multi-colored overlays. A white and light yellow sole with multicolor speckle details completes the design. The women's Nike Dunk Low SE Easter Candy (W) released in June of 2021 and retailed for $110.
